Package ro.isdc.wro.util

Interface Summary
Function<F,T> Determines an output value based on an input value.
ObjectDecorator<T> Describe a class which acts as a decorator.
ObjectFactory<T> Classic factory interface.
Ordered Classes implementing this interface signal to the classes that load them that order is significant.
Transformer<T> Transform some an object of some type to another object of the same type.
 

Class Summary
AbstractDecorator<T> Templated decorator.
Base64 Encodes and decodes to and from Base64 notation.
Base64.InputStream A Base64.InputStream will read data from another java.io.InputStream, given in the constructor, and encode/decode to/from Base64 notation on the fly.
Base64.OutputStream A Base64.OutputStream will write data to another java.io.OutputStream, given in the constructor, and encode/decode to/from Base64 notation on the fly.
DestroyableLazyInitializer<T> A subclass of LazyInitializer allows to destroy the created object.
LazyInitializer<T> A clone of LazyInitializer, which doesn't throw any checked exception when get method is invoked.
ProxyFactory<T> An ObjectFactory used to create Proxy for objects initialized by provided LazyInitializer's.
RegexpProperties Used to overcome the limitation of Properties class when dealing with regular expressions read from properties file.
SchedulerHelper Encapsulates the logic which handles scheduler creation and destroy.
StopWatch Simple stop watch, allowing for timing of a number of tasks, exposing total running time and running time for each named task.
StopWatch.TaskInfo Inner class to hold data about one task executed within the stop watch.
StringUtils StringUtils Utility class.
Transformers Contains factory methods for creating Transformer object.
WroTestUtils WroTestUtils.
WroUtil Utility class.
